title: Kim Kardashian camps out for baby shower - This is Local London
text:
Kim Kardashian was joined by her famous sisters for a baby shower that turned into something of a pyjama party. The reality TV star, 35, is expecting her second child with rapper husband Kanye West, and celebrated the impending birth with a Troop Beverly Hills-themed bash.
 This is Local London.
